title: A Story About Treating a Female Knight, Who Has Never Been Treated as a Woman, as a Woman
description: Female knight Leo has never had ladylike qualities, she's a soldier through and through, adorned with scars and rock hard abs to match. She's never really been treated as a woman...until one day the magician Fooly confesses his love for everything about her. These two will challenge the quest named "Romance," which is tougher to complete than a super hard dungeon! How will our steel-willed protagonist act in the face of love?
